  "title": "Explore more on Time, Distance, and Speed.",
  "body": " Explore more on Time, Distance, and Speed     Explore the concept of average speed and how it relates to time and distance with this interactive video.     Explore more on the concept of Acceleration, which is the rate of change of velocity with respect to time.      "
